HEADWORD: Beau monde
<hw>Beau` monde"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[F. <ets>beau</ets> fine
+ <ets>monde</ets> world.]</ety> <def>The fashionable world; people of
fashion and gayety.</def> <rj><au>Prior.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
